Justin Bartha https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Bartha 0 Justin Lee Bartha (born July 21, 1978) is an American actor, known for his roles as Riley Poole in the National Treasure film series, Doug Billings in The Hangover trilogy, and David Sawyer in the NBC comedy series The New Normal. He currently stars as Colin Morrello in the CBS All Access legal and political drama The Good Fight.
